Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.92,Staff,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕来源：动音漫影 & 极影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:04.88,Staff,NTP,0,0,0,,片源：R2JRAW  翻译：荷伊 & SS  后期：kenan2763
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信别人也不会有什么好结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要自己活着不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己活着不就得了吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.30,0:01:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在浓烟的包围中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五人与渐渐逼近的死亡拼命搏斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要死在这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.76,0:02:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木现在...应该就在二舍六房里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的啊 阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道想硬生生的把门打开？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拼命撞了半天都纹丝不动的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴！臭小鬼们！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为这点事就放弃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的命可没有那么贱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是...六房的钥匙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,省得我自己找了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 野本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 樱木进去救他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？去那里边？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在操场看到樱木时 还觉得误算了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊 他自己进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来只要处理掉那钥匙 这事就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 这钥匙请借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 野本 你该不会以为我不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这火灾的原因...就是你的烟头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕 没事的 我不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要装什么都不知道就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是相信你的 你也相信我就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 把钥匙给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来不相信任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得只要自己活着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那些家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是我这辈子第一次得到的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这辈子第一次得到的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 小鬼就是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来以为你应该更聪明点的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好经打的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也罢 看那火肯定没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我下地狱吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥！阿哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我啊！阿哥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥的脚...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没希望了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 阿哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖累了阿哥 对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么早放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬着从石原那里抢来的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常露馅向着六房拼命奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是和他们在一起 活着也没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常露馅第一次发自内心地这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我 快救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！元鱼！你打算就死在这里啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈！你不想再见你妹了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵哥！卷心菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死啊！怎么能白白死在这种地方啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来 大家起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常露馅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家...都是因为我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来对你来说太重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 卷心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能光让你一个人耍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.95,0:08:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了啊 常露馅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走！快出去避难！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 我怎么可能扔下阿哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会这样死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走啊 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍什么帅啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥 这不像你会说的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是跟阿哥学的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一个一个的 都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六房的人好像没来得及逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那样子...是没救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了！樱木死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你活该 樱木！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱 樱木...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害我好担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 野本 呐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石原老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...这火灾的起因...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住 石原
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次可不会这样就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肺在浓烟中被炙烤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差点被蔓延的大火烧死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个人的心紧紧地抱成了一团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔阂也好 猜忌也好 全都被大火烧尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 石原依然用歹毒的蛇眼盯着阿哥不放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小池小姐 接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉 樱木君 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真理雄呢？常露馅没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元鱼？丈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 有事的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧伤 加上砸伤 左脚骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏迷了整整一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们...他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你好好躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都跟现在的你一样 很拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚷着救救阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的血要多少给你们多少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还追着医生 让他保证一定要救活你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们真的很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我这种渣滓一样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱木君...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的老爹...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真理雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我...杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六郎太 妈妈就拜托给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹是名军人 我很尊敬 崇拜他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 上了火线的老爹到战败仍然去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的五个哥哥全都战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下我和老妈两人 拼命地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着这个去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在工作结束后 都有去练拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你父亲一样 一旦决定了劝也劝不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对...会还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你一百倍...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从被扣留了八年的西伯利亚回来的老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅外貌 所有的一切都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去工作 每天只会借酒消愁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动不动就对我和母亲大吼大叫的老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经不是以前的老爹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不忍心看着这样的老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都拼命练拳击到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在我的出道赛定下来的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱还来喝酒 别再来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拳击？那不是美国佬的玩意儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 我只是...想像爸和哥哥们那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为一个坚强的男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为打拳击就能变得比我强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 还击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可还不会输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底回来干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.87,0:16:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了让我和妈看到你这副落魄的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才特地回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人心寒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六郎太 你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈就拜托给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹成了死尸在河边被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想起来 五个儿子都战死疆场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己一人苟活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这份罪恶感 改变了老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有工作 也无法适应战后剧变的社会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对那样的老爹 我却丢给他一些最无情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他逼到了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至没有尝试去理解老爹的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...等于是我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再失去我珍重的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 杀了父母是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵～这是慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 那是从哪拿过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉在隔壁的病房里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个手脚不干净的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 是真的掉在那的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能掉在病房里啊 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我白痴是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实...这次的火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听啊 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿哥...大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽血的时候不也哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也是因为血型跟阿哥不符才...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...不准说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 刚才不是跟你说好了的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探望的时间到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在通融5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那阿哥 再见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 稍微休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒吧 他们...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们 都是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他值得我们相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等阿哥伤好出院后就差不多该出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.91,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六个人知道了阿哥心中也有道很深的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤势痊愈后 阿哥就能精神抖擞地出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就轮到自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六人心中都充满了希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄逼近的暗影 短暂的平静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人把将来的梦想刻在了树上
